'''Fred Blanchard''' is an illustrator who has worked on several ''Star Wars'' comics.

He illustrated the [[Heir to the Empire (comics)|''Heir to the Empire'']] comic book adaptation and provided illustrations for the French [[roleplaying game]] magazine [[Casus Belli (magazine)|''Casus Belli'']].{{Mediacat|imagecat=images by Fred Blanchard}}

